h1 AnimatedGifs plugin
p Adds support for resizing animated gifs. Once added, animated gifs will be resized while maintaining all animated frames. By default, .NET only saves the first frame of the GIF image.
p Best used with disk caching, as large animations can take a while to process (sometimes even over a second).

