h2#installation Installation
p
  | Either run
  code Install-Package ImageResizer.Plugins.AnimatedGifs
  | in the NuGet package manager, or:
ol
  li Add ImageResizer.Plugins.AnimatedGifs to your project
  li
    | Add
    code &lt;add name="AnimatedGifs" /&gt;
    | inside
    code &lt;resizer&gt;&lt;plugins&gt;&lt;/plugins&gt;&lt;/resizer&gt;
    | in Web.config.
